  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">YOGI Tea Diversification pilot Phase 1 - Rwanda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This consultancy will involve a partnership with YogiTea, a company that source tea and associated products from Rwanda. PAC will run a action research pilot, working with a small group of farmers to assess agricultural diversification options that will increase incomes and utilize regenerative agriculture approaches. PAC will work with a local consulting firm on the delivery of this. 
The first stage of this will be a scoping study which will result in the design of the pilot.</narrative>
